Cell["\<\
Run the cell below to get the heuristic approximations for Bc as a function \
of the parameters: Bc = Bc(\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Floor\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] or \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Ceiling\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], N, \[Mu], qmin)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9887720919458313`*^9, 3.9887722188441906`*^9}},
